(275, 76, 6, '1994-09-22', 'Season six of Seinfeld, an American comedy television series created by Jerry Seinfeld and Larry David, began airing on September 22, 1994, and concluded on May 18, 1995, on NBC. Season six placed first in the Nielsen ratings above Home Improvement and ER.', 'seinfeld-1400_6.jpg', 3634, '2020-11-27 11:48:57', NULL),
